original_title: I Do Bidoo Bidoo: Heto nApo sila!
overview: Rock Polotan and Tracy Fuentebella are teenage sweethearts and both nursing students in a university in Manila are in love and full of dreams. A youthful indiscretion leads them to early parenthood, a situation they face squarely, and quite maturely, by planning to get married. They shortly realize, however, that the problem behind their wedding plans has less to do with themselves than with their own parents.
title: I Do Bidoo Bidoo: Heto nApo sila!
